#: .\TALK_EMERGENCY.json
msgid ""
"[ON FIRE]  AAAuuuugh, <swear!>!  I'm on fire!  Don't just stand there, "
"<name_b>.  Help put me out."
msgstr "[着火] 啊啊啊，<swear!>！我着火了！别光站着，<name_b>。快来帮我灭火。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid "[POLICE] Officer, with all this trouble, I could use some assistance."
msgstr "[警察] 警官，现在这么乱，我需要些帮助。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid ""
"[BADGE] Well, fellow police person.  We need to team up to, like, fight "
"crime and stuff."
msgstr "[警徽] 嘿，警察同僚。我们得组队，比如，打击犯罪什么的。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid "[DOCTOR] Because we should work together to help the injured."
msgstr "[医生] 因为我们应该一起帮助伤员。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid ""
"[MEDICAL]  It's because I'm sick, doc.  You gotta help me get through this."
msgstr "[医疗] 因为我病了，医生。你得帮我挺过去。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid ""
"[MARTIAL ARTS] A rival school, eh?  We'll see who's the strongest.  Prepare "
"yourself for battle!"
msgstr "[武术] 敌对流派，嗯？我们来看看谁最强。准备战斗吧！"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid "[FANCY] Because you seem legit.  Wanna roll with my squad?"
msgstr "[时髦] 因为你看起来挺靠谱的。想加入我的小队吗？"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid "[GUITAR] These roads are mighty long and lonesome."
msgstr "[吉他] 这些路又长又寂寞。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid "[POWER ARMOR] Because I'm the dude in power armor."
msgstr "[动力装甲] 因为我是穿动力装甲的家伙。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid ""
"[CANNIBAL] There's no need to be ashamed, <name_g>.  And no need to go "
"hungry.  Bon Appetit."
msgstr "[食人者] 不必感到羞耻，<name_g>。也不必挨饿。祝你好胃口。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT.json
msgid ""
"[PSYCHO] You can eat whoever you want as long as it's not me.  I don't "
"really care."
msgstr "[精神变态] 只要不吃我，你想吃谁都行。我其实不在乎。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid ""
"[ALPHA 100%] Come, brother, we must work together to forge a new world."
msgstr "[阿尔法 100%] 来吧，兄弟，我们必须携手打造一个新世界。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[BEAST 100%] Another predator!  Let the hunt begin!"
msgstr "[野兽 100%] 又一个掠食者！让狩猎开始吧！"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[BIRD 100%] The great migration has begun."
msgstr "[鸟类 100%] 伟大的迁徙已经开始了。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[BOVINE 100%] Come, join the herd before you're left behind."
msgstr "[牛类 100%] 来吧，在被落下之前加入兽群。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[CEPHALOPOD 100%] Finally, someone worth talking to."
msgstr "[头足类 100%] 终于，有个值得交谈的人了。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[CHAOS 100%] One is a monster. Two is an army."
msgstr "[混沌 100%] 一个是怪物。两个就是一支军队。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[FEY 100%] Shall we form a bond?"
msgstr "[仙灵 100%] 我们缔结盟约如何？"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[FELINE 100%] Hungry. Sleepy. Hungry?"
msgstr "[猫科 100%] 饿了。困了。又饿了？"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid ""
"[AQUATIC 100%] It's dry and bright here.  Let's leave this harsh desert "
"behind."
msgstr "[水生 100%] 这里又干又亮。让我们离开这片严酷的沙漠吧。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[INSECT 100%] You must serve the queen."
msgstr "[昆虫 100%] 你必须侍奉女王。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[LIZARD 100%] I hunger for meat.  How will you help feed me?"
msgstr "[蜥蜴 100%] 我渴望吃肉。你打算怎么帮我填饱肚子？"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[WOLF 100%] Take your place among the pack."
msgstr "[狼 100%] 在狼群中占据一席之地吧。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[PROTOTYPE 100%] Let's see just how much we can improve ourselves."
msgstr "[原型 100%] 让我们看看我们能将自己提升到何种程度。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[DIMINUTIVE 100%] Safety?  Danger?  Let's flee."
msgstr "[微小 100%] 安全？危险？我们快逃吧。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[MYCUS 100%] WE are the Mycus."
msgstr "[真菌 100%] 我们即是真菌。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid ""
"[PLANT 100%] Let's take root before the fertile lands are claimed by others."
msgstr "[植物 100%] 让我们在肥沃的土地被他人占据前扎根于此。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[RAPTOR 100%] Shall we do battle or join together?"
msgstr "[猛禽 100%] 我们是该战斗，还是联合？"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid ""
"[RAT 100%] Finally. Someone as sensible and handsome as myself.  It's about "
"time."
msgstr "[鼠类 100%] 终于来了。一个像我一样理智又英俊的家伙。是时候了。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid ""
"[AQUEOUS 100%] Are we still separate entities?  It's confusing sometimes."
msgstr "[水栖 100%] 我们仍然是独立的个体吗？有时真让人困惑。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[ARACHNID 100%] We can't prey on our own kind, now, can we?"
msgstr "[蛛形 100%] 我们不能捕食同类，对吧？"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[SUBTERRANEAN 100%] The dark caves await us."
msgstr "[地下 100%] 黑暗的洞穴正等待着我们。"

#: .\TALK_RECRUIT_THRESH.json
msgid "[BEAR 100%] We must feed before winter."
msgstr "[熊类 100%] 我们必须在冬天来临前吃饱。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Extinguishing Fire"
msgstr "扑灭火势"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Extinguishing Fire'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You are on fire, and someone or something is helping put you out."
msgstr "你着火了，有人或什么东西正在帮你灭火。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Extinguishing Fire'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "It burns! Put out that fire!"
msgstr "烧起来了！快把火扑灭！"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "NPC Recruitment Options"
msgstr "NPC招募选项"

#. ~ Description for NPC Recruitment Options
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Gives special recruitment dialog if your character and an NPC have certain "
"traits, stats, effects, or gear.  Post-threshold mutants will always join "
"their own kind."
msgstr "如果你的角色和NPC拥有特定特质、属性、效果或装备，将提供特殊招募对话。阈值后的突变体总会加入同类。"
